questions.quote: Thank you, Dr. Phillips, but I'm having my lunch at this table, here in the middle. I'm having lunch right here, with my good friend Joey, if he'll sit with me.
Yes! I'm fine. In fact I've been fine for a long time now and I think, the reason is you.
Well maybe it's cold in there. Or maybe I screwed up the first date I had in 9 years.
Okay, look you wanna hold onto your food? You gotta scare people off. I learned that living on the street.
I know. I know. Oh God. There's no tissue! Can you grab me some toilet paper?
Nope, sound like me. Pheebs, it's going great. Look at Chandler with little baby girl Chandler.
You know Pheebs, when I was little, on my birthday, my daddy would hide a present in every room of the house, and then he would draw a treasure map to help me find 'em all.
Yeah, but you can come and visit me. I bet that you could uh, own a few places down there.
How 'bout instead you, go get changed! You, give him back his underwear! I'm gonna go get a cab, and I want everyone down stairs in two minutes! Monica!
Oh, umm, Joey was born, and then 28 years later, I was robbed!!
